        "created_at": "2025-02-22T18:25:29.016Z",
        "cooked": "<p>The app is claustrophobic upon open.</p>\n<p>It should display the search bar or pinned chats (can we also get pinned chats?) to start. Right off the jump the top message is crammed up top and feels unnatural. Matching the look/feel of iMessage or WhatsApp are good case studies.<br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/f/d/fd589a1e237652b1ac2130be2d033b3b92a52bf5.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/fd589a1e237652b1ac2130be2d033b3b92a52bf5\" title=\"IMG_0845\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/f/d/fd589a1e237652b1ac2130be2d033b3b92a52bf5_2_229x500.jpeg\" alt=\"IMG_0845\" data-base62-sha1=\"A9cCZNNEUFf0LsDHcEgvARIK1bn\" width=\"229\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/f/d/fd589a1e237652b1ac2130be2d033b3b92a52bf5_2_229x500.jpeg, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/f/d/fd589a1e237652b1ac2130be2d033b3b92a52bf5_2_343x750.jpeg 1.5x, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/f/d/fd589a1e237652b1ac2130be2d033b3b92a52bf5_2_458x1000.jpeg 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"101010\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">IMG_0845</span><span class=\"informations\">1206×2622 297 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p>Surprised nobody has mentioned this yet but worth starting a conversation.</p>",
