        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"unknpwn\" data-post=\"1\" data-topic=\"67117\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/u/ce73a5/48.png\" class=\"avatar\"> unknpwn:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>can we also get pinned chats?</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Yes you can, you can pin up to four chats.</p>\n<p>Also I don’t see any issues with it, just scroll a little bit down and the search bar appears.</p>",
