        "cooked": "<p>Thanks for the quick reply Meg!</p>\n<p>I’ve heard common sentiments anecdotally in my social circles as well. I feel like pinning in the same style as iMessage would also be an improvement. They take up less visual real estate as a “collapsed circle” than keeping the entire entry stuck in place.</p>\n<p>All minor QOL of course.</p>",
